#: ../../glossary/secrets.rst:7
msgid ""
"Encrypted Secrets allow you to pass private data to your apps, like API "
"keys, access tokens, database passwords, or other credentials, in a "
"secure way without exposing them in your code. Secrets provide you with a"
" secure way to store this data in a way that is accessible to Apps so "
"that they can authenticate third-party services/solutions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../glossary/secrets.rst:11
