msgid ""
"Add the secret to your profile on lightning.ai. Log in to your "
"lightning.ai account > **Profile** > **Secrets** tab > click the **+New**"
" button. Provide a name and value to your secret, for example, name could"
" be \"github_api_token\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../glossary/secrets.rst:22
msgid ""
"Secret names must start with a letter and can only contain letters, "
"numbers, dashes, and periods. The Secret names must comply with `RFC1123 "
"naming conventions <https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1123>`_. The Secret"
" value has no restrictions."
msgstr ""

